	<item>
		<title>Get started with Instagram Automation</title>
		<link>https://docs.chatrace.com/kb/instagram-automation/</link>
					<comments>https://docs.chatrace.com/kb/instagram-automation/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Team]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 03 Jul 2021 14:16:47 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid isPermaLink="false">https://docs.chatrace.com/?post_type=kb&#038;p=1883</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Instagram Automation allows Instagram Businesses to use a chatbot to manage their Instagram DMs. An Instagram Business Account must be connected to a Facebook Page for Instagram automation]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Instagram Automation allows Instagram Businesses to use a chatbot to manage their Instagram DMs. An Instagram Business Account must be connected to a Facebook Page for Instagram automation to work.</p>



<p></p>



<p>Instagram Automation is available for the following accounts:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list" style="line-height:1">
<li style="line-height:2">Any Instagram Professional account for a business.</li>



<li style="line-height:1">Any Instagram Professional account for a Creator.</li>
</ul>



<div style="height:57px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p>To manage Instagram messages via Chatrace, Instagram business accounts must enable the connected tools to toggle under message control settings. </p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1024" height="665" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/161856968_298941651650715_9153695413459699473_n-1024x665.png" alt="" class="wp-image-1945" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/161856968_298941651650715_9153695413459699473_n-1024x665.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/161856968_298941651650715_9153695413459699473_n-300x195.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/161856968_298941651650715_9153695413459699473_n-768x499.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/161856968_298941651650715_9153695413459699473_n.png 1340w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Connect your Instagram Professional account to Chatrace.</h4>



<p>Go to the <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://chatrace.com/en/new-bot" target="_blank">Sign-Up</a> page and choose Instagram.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="632" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-8-1024x632.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2482" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-8-1024x632.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-8-300x185.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-8-768x474.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-8.png 1397w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p></p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">How to build Instagram flows </h4>



<p>The process of building flows for all channels is the same. We recommend you always use the <strong>Omnichannel</strong> message type.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="559" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-10-1024x559.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2484" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-10-1024x559.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-10-300x164.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-10-768x419.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/image-10.png 1452w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p><br></p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="limitations">Important Notes</h4>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Your Instagram Business account must be connected to a Facebook Page.</li>



<li>Group threads (conversations with more than 2 participants) are not supported.</li>



<li>Instagram Comment Automation tool doesn&#8217;t work on Instagram Ads.</li>
</ul>
]]></content:encoded>
					
