										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>This feature allows you to automatically reply to replies on your Instagram Story. </p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe loading="lazy" title="How to set up Instagram story automation" width="780" height="439" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/iTpRGKEQrcM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Create Instagram Story Automation</h4>



<p><strong>Click on Tools &gt;&gt; Instagram Story Automation &gt;&gt; Click on &#8216;Add New&#8217; &amp; name your Instagram Story Automation.</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="495" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-52-1024x495.png" alt="" class="wp-image-3221" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-52-1024x495.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-52-300x145.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-52-768x371.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-52-1536x743.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-52.png 1870w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="495" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_224911261-1024x495.png" alt="" class="wp-image-3222" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_224911261-1024x495.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_224911261-300x145.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_224911261-768x371.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_224911261-1536x743.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_224911261.png 1870w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p><strong>You can track replies on all your Instagram Stories or a Specific Story.</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="495" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_225347644-1024x495.png" alt="" class="wp-image-3224" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_225347644-1024x495.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_225347644-300x145.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_225347644-768x371.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_225347644-1536x743.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_225347644.png 1870w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p><strong>You can reply with a Text or with a Flow.</strong></p>



<p><strong><em>Reply with Text</em></strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="495" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-54-1024x495.png" alt="" class="wp-image-3225" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-54-1024x495.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-54-300x145.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-54-768x371.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-54-1536x743.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-54.png 1870w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p><strong><em>Reply with a Flow</em></strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="495" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-55-1024x495.png" alt="" class="wp-image-3226" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-55-1024x495.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-55-300x145.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-55-768x371.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-55-1536x743.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-55.png 1870w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="495" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_230455004-1024x495.png" alt="" class="wp-image-3228" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_230455004-1024x495.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_230455004-300x145.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_230455004-768x371.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_230455004-1536x743.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-14_230455004.png 1870w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p><strong>After setting up your Instagram Story Automation, click on Save &amp; Turn ON your Instagram Story Automation.</strong></p>



