		<item>
		<title>How to auto-reply to Instagram Story Mention</title>
		<link>https://docs.chatrace.com/kb/how-to-automatically-respond-to-instagram-story-mention/</link>
					<comments>https://docs.chatrace.com/kb/how-to-automatically-respond-to-instagram-story-mention/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Oluwafemi Lawrence]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 15 Feb 2023 20:31:25 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid isPermaLink="false">https://docs.chatrace.com/?post_type=kb&#038;p=2703</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Instagram Story Mention Reply is an important feature that helps businesses automatically reply/send a message whenever someone mentions your business in their Instagram story. Setup]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p><strong>Instagram Story Mention Reply</strong> is an important feature that helps businesses automatically reply/send a message whenever someone mentions your business in their Instagram story.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe loading="lazy" title="How to Create Story Mention Reply for Instagram" width="780" height="439" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gB4C0jU2x3U?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Setup Instagram Story Mention Automation</h4>



<p>Follow the steps below to set up Instagram Story Mention on your Instagram Bot.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Create your Instagram Story Mention Flow (Message type must be &#8216;Instagram&#8217; &amp; make sure you publish your flow)</strong></li>
</ul>



