		<item>
		<title>How to set up Conversation starters?</title>
		<link>https://docs.chatrace.com/kb/conversation-starters/</link>
					<comments>https://docs.chatrace.com/kb/conversation-starters/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Team]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 14 Feb 2020 09:40:22 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid isPermaLink="false">https://docs.chatrace.com/?post_type=kb&#038;p=546</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Conversation Starters allow users to start a conversation with a business with a list of frequently asked questions. Users will see questions about your business]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Conversation Starters allow users to start a conversation with a business with a list of frequently asked questions. Users will see questions about your business instead of the generic &#8220;Get Started&#8221; button. We recommend you use the Conversation Starters feature to help your users/audience start a conversation with your business.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe loading="lazy" title="How to create Conversation Starter" width="780" height="439" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vReLo8ZQnwE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">How to create Conversation Starters?</h4>



<p>To create a Conversation Starter for your business, Navigate to Menu &gt; Settings &gt; Channels (Messenger/Instagram) &gt; Conversation Starter and click the “Edit” button.</p>



<p></p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="460" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-21_015457258-1024x460.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2752" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-21_015457258-1024x460.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-21_015457258-300x135.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-21_015457258-768x345.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-21_015457258-1536x690.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-21_015457258.png 1896w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>


<p>Input your business&#8217;s frequently asked questions, set the response flow, click on the + icon to add it and click on save on the top right corner.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="498" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-9-1024x498.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2753" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-9-1024x498.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-9-300x146.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-9-768x373.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-9-1536x747.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-9.png 1903w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="497" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-10_220851540-1024x497.png" alt="" class="wp-image-3071" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-10_220851540-1024x497.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-10_220851540-300x146.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-10_220851540-768x373.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-10_220851540-1536x746.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image_2023-06-10_220851540.png 1889w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p></p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
